attributes.name: Ivy Mini-Bag S Grey
attributes.description: How about this new model from the Ivy series? The classic, modern shape, the round handle and the soft, detachable shoulder straps make this lovely Ivy bag from AIGNER stand out. The bag is available in several colours so this mini bag can be combined perfectly with anything. See for yourself how beautiful this everyday accessory is.

customFields.product_details_:
• Extra shoulder strap length: 45-64 cm, adjustable
  • Handle height: 10 cm
  • 1 zipper compartment
  • 1 key strap
  • Protective feet on the bottom
  • Light gold hardware
  • Measurement: H 21cm x W 25 cm x D 10 cm
